PermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/yellen-says-chinese-response-possible-expected-us-tariff-action-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>麦当劳在报告食品问题后与中国监管机构合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-cooperating-with-chinese-regulator-after-reported-food-issues-2024-05-13/</link><description>麦当劳周一在其中文网站上表示，该公司正在积极配合中国当地市场监管机构对食品问题相关事宜进行调查核实。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 14:55:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/mcdonalds-cooperating-with-chinese-regulator-after-reported-food-issues-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将放弃对中国竞标罗马尼亚太阳能园区的调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-drop-probe-into-chinese-bidders-romanian-solar-park-2024-05-13/</link><description>欧洲工业委员会蒂埃里·布雷顿(Thierry Breton)周一表示，在中国企业退出罗马尼亚太阳能园区公开招标后，欧盟委员会将结束对这些公司的调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:38:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/eu-drop-probe-into-chinese-bidders-romanian-solar-park-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国新冠举报人入狱四年后将获释</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-covid-whistleblower-due-release-after-4-years-jail-2024-05-13/</link><description>预计中国当局将于周一释放一名被判入狱四年的公民记者，她记录了 2020 年中部城市武汉冠状病毒爆发的早期阶段。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 12:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-covid-whistleblower-due-release-after-4-years-jail-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国本周启动1万亿元刺激性债券发行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-kick-off-1-trillion-yuan-stimulus-bond-issues-this-week-2024-05-13/</link><description>中国财政部计划本周开始筹集期待已久的1万亿元人民币（合1380亿美元）的长期特别国债，以筹集资金用于刺激疲软经济的关键领域。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 11:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-kick-off-1-trillion-yuan-stimulus-bond-issues-this-week-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>ESR表示已收到投资者团体的私有化提案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/esr-halts-trading-potential-take-private-plan-sources-say-2024-05-13/</link><description>目前估值为 54 亿美元的香港上市房地产基金管理公司 ESR Group 周一停止了股票交易，称一群投资者已提议将其私有化。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 10:42:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/esr-halts-trading-potential-take-private-plan-sources-say-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>付费订阅强劲增长，腾讯音乐第一季度收入超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencent-music-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-05-13/</link><description>得益于其类似 Spotify 的音乐流媒体平台上付费订阅和广告服务的强劲增长，中国腾讯音乐娱乐集团周一第一季度收入超出预期。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 09:08:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencent-music-beats-quarterly-revenue-estimates-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>三名男子在英国法庭出庭，被控帮助香港外国情报部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-charge-three-men-with-helping-hong-kongs-foreign-intelligence-service-2024-05-13/</link><description>三名被控协助香港驻英国外国情报部门的男子周一在伦敦一家法院出庭，此前他们在英国各地遭到一系列逮捕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 07:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-police-charge-three-men-with-helping-hong-kongs-foreign-intelligence-service-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>“选择法国”投资推动承诺创纪录的 160 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/france-gets-16-billion-foreign-investments-part-choose-france-event-2024-05-13/</link><description>周一，法国赢得了创纪录的 150 亿欧元（161.7 亿美元）外国投资承诺，让法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 得以在全球首席执行官的聚光灯下，暂时忘记紧张的公共财政和疲弱的民意调查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 04:03:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/france-gets-16-billion-foreign-investments-part-choose-france-event-2024-05-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行承诺支持经济复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</link><description>中国央行周五表示，将确保流动性合理充裕和信贷扩张，巩固经济复苏，但经济复苏仍面临诸多挑战。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:17:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-central-bank-pledges-support-economic-recovery-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>独家：Shein 在美国上市遇到障碍的情况下加紧伦敦 IPO 准备工作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</link><description>消息人士称，如果此次IPO成功，可能会成为今年全球规模最大的IPO之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/shein-steps-up-london-ipo-preparations-amid-us-hurdles-listing-sources-say-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车制造商 Zeekr 在美国市场首次亮相，股价飙升近 35%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五，Zeekr 的股价较首次公开募股价格上涨近 35%，这为这家电动汽车制造商带来了强劲的开局，这是自 2021 年以来首家中国公司在美国主要市场首次亮相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 10:48:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-zeekr-set-debut-nyse-after-upsized-ipo-2024-05-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>